    <briefdescription>
<para>Unique type identifier for engine resources. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1world_1_1types_1_1ManagerTypeId" kindref="compound">ManagerTypeId</ref> assigns a unique, monotonically increasing integer ID to each resource type at compile time. Used by <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1world_1_1ResourceRegistry" kindref="compound">ResourceRegistry</ref> as an index into the `fastAccess_` array for O(1) type-based resource lookup.</para>
<para>All resource categories (Managers, CommandBuffers, CommandHandlers) share a single index space.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1world_1_1ResourceRegistry" kindref="compound">ResourceRegistry</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
